            "id": "s_l3_1",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Gathering Leftovers 🧹",
            "content": "What if you don't know how many arguments a function will receive?\n\nUse the **Rest Parameter** `...`."
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l3_2",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Example 🎒",
            "content": "It collects all remaining arguments into an ARRAY.",
            "codeSnippet": "function sum(...numbers) {\n  let total = 0;\n  for (let n of numbers) {\n    total += n;\n  }\n  return total;\n}\n\nconsole.log(sum(1, 2, 3, 4)); // 10",
            "codeLanguage": "javascript",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
